OL,3,CYour Wales Weather Team
OL,5,FRuth Dodsworth
OL,7,FRuth is one of Wales' best known
OL,8,Ffaces, having been on your screens for
OL,9,Falmost 25 years! An award-winning
OL,10,Fjournalist, Ruth began her career as a
OL,11,Fnewsroom reporter and quickly went on
OL,12,Fto present a whole host of programmes
OL,13,Ffor ITV Wales. A switch to weather
OL,14,Fcame in 2000, allowing Ruth to expand
OL,15,Fher interest in meteorology and
OL,16,Fclimate change. Ruth is also able to
OL,17,Findulge her love of the great outdoors
OL,18,Fas the presenter of Coast and Country.
