OL,3,CYour Wales Weather Team
OL,5,F"I can honestly say that I have the
OL,6,Fbest job in the world. I get to live
OL,7,Fand work in the most beautiful
OL,8,Fcountry, and I get to meet the people
OL,9,Fthat make Wales the most wonderful
OL,10,Fplace."
OL,12,FRuth is a proud Ambassador for Cancer
OL,13,FResearch Wales, and a Patron of the
OL,14,FDomestic Abuse charity Hafan Cymru,
OL,15,Fcharities which are very close to her
OL,16,Fheart.
